Class Round

  • java.lang.Object
    • evaluation.Round

    • Constructor Detail

      • Round

        public Round(int currentRound,
             java.io.File path,
             Player player1,
             Player player2,
             EvaluationManager manager)
        The constructor set all necessary variables, so that the basic information about this round are known.

        Parameters:
        currentRound - The round number in the run.
        path - A String thats is representing the path to the round directory, in which all Files for this round are saved.
        player1 - An object with the Player interface that possesses in this round the red pieces.
        player2 - An object with the Player interface that possesses in this round the red pieces.
        manager - A reference to the EvaluationManager.
